You can use 2 methods from the `String` class.

   - [**`String.contains()`**][1] which checks if the string contains a specified sequence of char values
   - [**`String.indexOf()`**][2] which returns the index within the string of the first occurence of the specified character or substring or returns -1 if the character is not found (there are 4 variations of this method)

