one more line 

    dependencies {
        compileOnly &#39;org.projectlombok:lombok:1.18.22&#39;
        annotationProcessor &#39;org.projectlombok:lombok:1.18.22&#39;
    }

With such combination you even don&#39;t need enabling *Annotation Processors* from @Vegard answer.

